{"tid":2181432,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"嘉湖山莊呎價跌穿9000元     套三房戶傳售566萬元","createTime":"2020-08-30T14:56:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T14:56:58.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b52b16de082b704ab4e261c3a189053840b852d6","tid":2181432,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T14:56:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ZGoL7X9uY70AzDuIybu_aw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/onccinstantnews.com/567b4a94eb22593295edafde592f24f9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FZGoL7X9uY70AzDuIybu_aw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2F567b4a94eb22593295edafde592f24f9&h=d75bc8b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=lPj0fEAhrWGYZLLoA4iNoPY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=aabd07a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】藍籌屋苑樓價進一步回落，天水圍嘉湖山莊呎價跌穿九千元。市場消息稱，屋苑樂湖居8座極低層B室，實用面積633方呎，套三房間隔，開價575萬元放售。由於單位內籠無裝修，加上位處極低層，市傳減至566萬元售出，呎價僅8,942元，料屬該盤今年最低呎價。據了解，今年1月該屋苑一個實用面積639方呎單位僅售575萬元，呎價8,998元屬對上低位。<br />\n<br />\n該盤套三房交投加快。祥益謝利官稱，同類型大單位過去10日連沽10伙，其中樂湖居10座中層A室，實用面積636方呎，一直為收租物業，剛交吉叫價670萬元放售，即有10組客睇樓，放盤即日售648萬元，呎價10,189元。該行稱，屋苑周末兩日錄9至10宗二手買賣。"}]}